00195 returnValue Options::ensureConsistency( )
00196 {
00197         /* flipping bounds require far bounds */
00198     /* (ckirches) Removed this as per filter's trust region
00199         if( enableFlippingBounds == BT_TRUE )
00200                 enableFarBounds = BT_TRUE;
00201     */
00202         
00203         if( enableDriftCorrection < 0 )
00204                 enableDriftCorrection = 0;
00205         
00206         if( enableCholeskyRefactorisation < 0 )
00207                 enableCholeskyRefactorisation = 0;
00208 
00209 
00210         if ( terminationTolerance <= 0.0 )
00211                 terminationTolerance = EPS;
00212 
00213         if ( epsIterRef <= 0.0 )
00214                 epsIterRef = EPS;
00215 
00216         if ( epsRegularisation <= 0.0 )
00217                 epsRegularisation = EPS;
00218 
00219         if ( boundTolerance <= 0.0 )
00220                 boundTolerance = EPS;
00221 
00222         if ( boundRelaxation <= 0.0 )
00223                 boundRelaxation = EPS;
00224         
00225         if ( maxPrimalJump <= 0.0 )
00226                 maxPrimalJump = EPS;
00227 
00228         if ( maxDualJump <= 0.0 )
00229                 maxDualJump = EPS;
00230 
00231 
00232         if ( initialRamping < 0.0 )
00233                 initialRamping = 0.0;
00234 
00235         if ( finalRamping < 0.0 )
00236                 finalRamping = 0.0;
00237 
00238         if ( initialFarBounds <= boundRelaxation )
00239                 initialFarBounds = boundRelaxation+EPS;
00240         
00241         if ( growFarBounds < 1.1 )
00242                 growFarBounds = 1.1;
00243 
00244         if ( epsFlipping <= 0.0 )
00245                 epsFlipping = EPS;
00246 
00247         if ( numRegularisationSteps < 0 )
00248                 numRegularisationSteps = 0;
00249 
00250         if ( epsRegularisation < 0.0 )
00251                 epsRegularisation = EPS;
00252 
00253         if ( numRefinementSteps < 0 )
00254                 numRefinementSteps = 0;
00255 
00256         if ( epsIterRef < 0.0 )
00257                 epsIterRef = EPS;
00258 
00259         if ( epsLITests < 0.0 )
00260                 epsLITests = EPS;
00261 
00262         if ( epsNZCTests < 0.0 )
00263                 epsNZCTests = EPS;
00264 
00265         return SUCCESSFUL_RETURN;
00266 }
